s be upon him, said, \u201cIf three people in a town or in the desert do not establish prayer among them, then Satan has overcome them. You must establish the congregation, for the wolf eats the isolated\u00a0sheep.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 547 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19899,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/09\/29\/enjoin-follow-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38878,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: I enjoin you to follow my companions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"I enjoin you to follow my companions, then those after them and those after them. Thereafter, falsehood will spread until a man offers his oath without being asked and a witness gives testimony without being asked. No\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36588,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/06\/khawarij-yoke-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":38878,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Khuruj: Rebels have rejected guidance of Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever secedes from the community as much as a handspan has thrown the yoke of Islam off of his neck.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4758 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0630\u064e\u0631\u0651\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17907,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/27\/sabr-with-sultan\/","url_meta":{"origin":38878,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sultan: Be patient with tyranny from your rulers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever sees something from his ruler that he hates, let him be patient. Whoever secedes from the community by as much as a handspan and dies will have died a death of ignorance.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":746,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/01\/do-not-point-weapon\/","url_meta":{"origin":38878,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Threats: Do not point a weapon at Muslims","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 1, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"None of you should point a weapon at his brother. Verily, he does not know if Satan will cause his hand to slip and thus he falls into a pit of fire.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 70